### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 2. Auth: Register
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "murat@test.com",
  "handle": "@murat",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Auth: Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "murat@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Store Token
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 4. Create Post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "NoSQL projesi harika ilerliyor! #NoSQL #P14 #Basari",
  "hashtags": ["NoSQL", "P14", "Basari"]
}

### 5. Engagement: Like
POST http://localhost:3000/engagements
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": "PASTE_POST_ID_HERE",
  "type": "like"
}

### 6. Analytics: Trending
GET http://localhost:3000/analytics/trending?period=hourly

### 7. Analytics: Influencers
GET http://localhost:3000/analytics/influencers

### 8. Analytics: Communities
GET http://localhost:3000/analytics/communities

### 9. User: Timeline
GET http://localhost:3000/users/PASTE_USER_ID_HERE/timeline

### 10. Hashtag: Time-Series
GET http://localhost:3000/hashtags/NoSQL/timeseries?from=2026-05-01&to=2026-05-07
